-- France Telecom Said to Be in Talks With Nouvel Obs on Le Monde Investment
-- Matthew Campbell
-- 2010-06-14T10:24:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/france-telecom-said-to-be-in-talks-with-nouvel-obs-on-le-monde-investment.html

          
          
             France Telecom SA is in discussions
with Nouvel Observateur Chief Executive Officer Claude Perdriel
that may result in a ‘minor’ investement by the phone company in
Le Monde, a person famililar with the situation said.  
 The outcome of the talks will depend on the timetable for
re-investment in the struggling French daily, said the person,
who declined to be identified because talks are private.  
          
          


  


        